    question: 'What practice areas are covered in the SQE2 assessment, and how long does it take to complete?',
    answer: '<p class="mb-4">\r\n' +
      '        The SQE2 assessment covers a broad range of practice areas to ensure that candidates are well-rounded and capable of handling various types of legal work. The key practice areas included in the assessment are carefully chosen to represent the core areas of legal practice that a newly qualified solicitor is likely to encounter.\r\n' +
