      '    <p class="mb-4">\r\n' +
      '        The marking process is standardized across all candidates, meaning that each task is scored in the same way, regardless of who the candidate is or where they took the exam. This standardization is crucial for maintaining the integrity of the assessment and ensuring that all candidates are judged on the same basis. To further ensure fairness, the examiners undergo regular training and calibration exercises to align their marking standards.\r\n' +
      '    </p>\r\n' +
      '    <h4 class="font-semibold my-4">Passing Score</h4>\r\n' +
      '    <p class="mb-4">\r\n' +
